description: [Raspberry Robin](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S1130) uses regsvr32.exe execution without any command line parameters for command and control requests to IP addresses associated with [Tor](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0183) nodes.(Citation: RedCanary RaspberryRobin 2022)

external_references.description: Lauren Podber and Stef Rand. (2022, May 5). Raspberry Robin gets the worm early. Retrieved May 17, 2024.
